:"2017-10-12T13:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最黎搵毒撚埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿仙奴=毒撚<br />\n巴=mk仔<br />\n車=有錢佬</blockquote><br />\n結果同有錢佬都係早結婚過毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e8c58aa13e837c42b2ca41997ff5e3ed363533","tid":433582,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:10:57.000Z","msg":"最愛果個可能不會陪你走到最後<br />\n<br />\n陪你走到最後果個可能唔係最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c9e9047a025e922073fa5131663bd4767c6c1e","tid":433582,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:12:34.000Z","msg":"搞咩今日咁sad牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97573442883aa7dcb6d9f445b7b83b0ae45278ea","tid":433582,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1d3c4b89ae3b95ea6a7f84ed33122d770713ac","tid":433582,"uid":121015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:20:20.000Z","msg":"好文"},{"pid":"5433d66c55a5b855fc4a1341716a2e2119c407ba","tid":433582,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:22:51.000Z","msg":"好撚似我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同個愛自己既女朋友一齊七年<br />\n但係最後都唔識珍惜佢<br />\n去左搵個所謂&quot;我愛的&quot;<br />\n最後都係冇好結果<br />\n好後悔<br />\n好想返返&quot;阿仙奴&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a4a93d6c99b10aab8abea47536ba6b707d8e71","tid":433582,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"@香川<br />\n@gap王"},{"pid":"03b3f5deb3349f155d7ad9aadb2bf8d5d07770c0","tid":433582,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"睇到我嘩嘩聲既傳波<br />\n咁多年得佢"},{"pid":"